---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <title>プロ講師指導塾｜家庭教師・個別指導・集団授業</title>

    <meta
      name="description"
      content="プロ講師による1対1の指導がメインで高校受験・大学受験の合格へのサポトートと学習管理の徹底を行います。"
    />
		<link rel="icon" href="/juku-logo.png" type="image/png" sizes="any">
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/juku-logo.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Anton&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<styles>
body {
  /* 通常フォント */
  font-family: 'Anton';
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: #000;
  background: pink;
}

html, body {
  height: 100%;
  -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
}

/* ==== 文字の書体を部分的に変更 === */
.gothic {
  font-family: 'Zen Maru Gothic', sans-serif;
}

.gothic-light {
  font-family: 'Zen Maru Gothic', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 500;
}


/* == ヘッダー == */
.header{
  display: flex;
  padding: 3px 10px;
  align-items: center;
}

.header img {
  height: 40px;
  width: 40px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  border: 1px solid;
}

.combi-text{
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  line-height: 1.3;
  margin: 0 0 0 10px;
  font-weight: 100;
}

.text-main{
  font-size: 20px;
  color: #000;
  display: block;
}

.text-sub{
  margin-left: 8px;
  font-size: 10px;
  color: #000;
  display: block;
}
</styles>
  </head>

	<body>
    <!-- ヘッダー -->
    <h1 class="header">
      <img src="/images/juku-logo.png" alt="logo">
      <span class="combi-text">
        <span class="text-sub">家庭教師・個別指導・集団授業</span>
        <span class="text-main">プロ講師指導塾</span>
      </span>  
     </h1> 
	</body>
</html>
